<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: #4f46e5; color: #fff; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
    .body { padding: 20px; background: #f9fafb; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
    .footer { text-align: center; padding: 15px; font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; }
    h1 { margin: 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to Our Blog!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <p>Hi <strong><%= name %></strong>,</p>
      <p>Thank you for registering at <strong>Blog</strong>! We're excited to have you on board.</p>
      <p>Your account details:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Name:</strong> <%= name %></li>
        <li><strong>Email:</strong> <%= email %></li>
        <li><strong>Joined:</strong> <%= joinedAt %></li>
      </ul>
      <p>Start exploring and sharing your thoughts with the community!</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br>Blog Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      &copy; <%= year %> Blog. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
